            <h1 class="display-4">Electric Vehicle Charging Stations</h1>
            <p class="lead">Powering the Future of Sustainable Transportation</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container my-5">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-8 offset-md-2">
                <h2 class="mb-4">What is an EV Charging Station?</h2>
                <p class="lead">An EV charging station is a dedicated infrastructure point where electric vehicles can recharge their batteries, similar to how traditional gas stations serve fuel-powered vehicles.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row mt-5">
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card card-charging h-100">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h3 class="card-title">Level 1 Charging</h3>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            - Standard 120V household outlet
                            - Slowest charging method
                            - Adds about 4-5 miles of range per hour
                            - Best for overnight or workplace charging
                            - Requires no special equipment beyond standard plug
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card card-charging h-100">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h3 class="card-title">Level 2 Charging</h3>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            - 240V charging (like dryer outlets)
                            - Faster charging speed
                            - Adds 25-30 miles of range per hour
                            - Common in public spaces, homes, and workplaces
                            - Requires professional installation
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card card-charging h-100">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h3 class="card-title">DC Fast Charging</h3>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            - High-power direct current charging
                            - Rapid charging method
                            - Adds 150-250 miles of range in 30 minutes
                            - Found at dedicated charging networks
                            - Best for long-distance travel
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row mt-5">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <h2 class="mb-4">Pricing Breakdown</h2>
                <table class="table table-striped">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>Charging Level</th>
                            <th>Typical Cost per kWh</th>
                            <th>Average Full Charge Cost</th>
                            <th>Charging Time</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td>Level 1 (Home)</td>
                            <td>$0.13</td>
                            <td>$2 - $5</td>
                            <td>20-24 hours</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>Level 2 (Public/Home)</td>
                            <td>$0.20 - $0.30</td>
                            <td>$6 - $12</td>
                            <td>4-10 hours</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>DC Fast Charging</td>
                            <td>$0.40 - $0.80</td>
                            <td>$10 - $30</td>
                            <td>20-40 minutes</td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row mt-5">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h2>Charging Network Comparison</h2>
                <ul class="list-group">
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>Tesla Supercharger</strong>
                        - Exclusive to Tesla vehicles
                        - Fastest charging speeds
                        - Widespread network coverage
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>ChargePoint</strong>
                        - Largest public charging network
                        - Compatible with most EV models
                        - Offers home and public charging solutions
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>Electrify America</strong>
                        - High-speed DC fast charging
                        - Growing nationwide network
                        - Supports multiple vehicle brands
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h2>Money-Saving Tips</h2>
                <ul class="list-group">
                    <li class="list-group-item">Charge during off-peak electricity hours</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">Use workplace or free public charging when possible</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">Install home solar to reduce charging costs</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">Compare charging network membership plans</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">Use charging apps to find most affordable stations</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
